e public, private and social sector who have distinguished themselves as ethical leaders of integrity and character while serving common good.\" The Leader of the Future Award is given for leadership required to move us into a future yet to be defined, according to the award's site. \"It is about values-based, diverse leaders of character who have the vision to see and the courage to shape the future.\"</p><p>In addition to Michael and Kass, who were honored for their work in the private sector, Philadelphia Police Commissioner Charles H. Ramsey from the public sector and General Peter W. Chiarelli, <a href=\"http://1mind4research.org/\" target=\"_blank\">CEO of One Mind for Research</a>, of the social sector were also given awards. All award-winners were honored at a dinner and award ceremony on October 16.</p><p>Frances Hesselbein, President and CEO of the Hesselbein Institute, said in a press release about the award, \"We are enthusiastic and privileged to have the opportunity to honor these humble and effective leaders who lead from the heart, have a clear mission and vision for the future, and have a deep respect for all people.\"</p><p>Previous winners of the award include Alan Mulally, President and CEO of the Ford Motor Company; Andrea Jung, Chair and CEO of Avon Products, Inc.; and A.G. Lafley, Chair and CEO of The Procter and Gamble Company.</p><p><a href=\"/newsroom/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Picture-0301.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-18994\" title=\"Picture 030\" src=\"/newsroom/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Picture-0301.jpg\" alt=\" \" width=\"590\" height=\"393\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"/newsroom/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Picture-0841.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-18995\" title=\"Picture 084\" src=\"/newsroom/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Picture-0841.jpg\" alt=\" \" width=\"590\" height=\"393\" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>All photos courtesy of Ben Asen Photography</p><p><em>You can read the <a href=\"http://www.hesselbeininstitute.org/about/press-releases/leaderofthefuture2012.html\" target=\"_blank\">entire press release here</a>. Read <a href=\"http://www.buddymedia.com/newsroom/2012/06/buddy-media-salesforce-acquisition/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Lazerow's reflections after selling Buddy Media</a> to Salesforce. If you want to learn more about the newest endeavor, the <a href=\"http://www.salesforce.com/marketing-cloud/overview/\" target=\"_blank\">Salesforce Marketing Cloud, you can learn more here</a>. </em></p>
